BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Open URL / Open URL With Selection

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: set mJson to do shell script "curl -s 'https://api.coinmarketcap.com/v1/ticker/vechain/'"set AppleScript's text item delimiters to {","}set keyValueList to (every text item in mJson) as listset AppleScript's text item delimiters to ""set theKeyValuePair to item 5 of keyValueListset AppleScript's text item delimiters to {": "}set theKeyValueBufferList to (every text item in theKeyValuePair) as listset AppleScript's text item delimiters to ""set theValue to item 2 of theKeyValueBufferListset value to do shell script "sed s/[^0-9.,]//g <<< " & theValuereturn "$" & value

BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Open URL / Open URL With Selection

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: set json to do shell script "curl -H 'CB-VERSION: 2015-04-08' https://api.coinbase.com/v2/prices/BTC-USD/spot"set json to do shell script "sed s/warnings.*//g <<< " & jsonset value to do shell script "sed s/[a-zA-Z:{},]//g <<< " & jsonreturn "$" & value
